<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Your OTP Code</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .container {
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 30px;
      max-width: 500px;
      margin: auto;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    h2 {
      color: #333;
    }
    .otp-box {
      background: #f0f8ff;
      color: #007bff;
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: bold;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      letter-spacing: 4px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    p {
      color: #555;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #999;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Hello <%= name %>,</h2>
    <p>We received a request to verify your email address. Please use the following One-Time Password (OTP) to complete your verification:</p>

    <div class="otp-box">
      <%= otp %>
    </div>

    <p>This OTP will expire in 5 minutes. If you didnâ€™t request this, you can safely ignore this email.</p>

    <div class="footer">
      &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Your Company Name. All rights reserved.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
